*Godina* je bila duga i teška. (The year was long and hard.)

*Godinu* dana smo čekali na rezultate. (We waited a year for the results.)

Posle više od *godinu* dana njihov se brak raspao. (After more than a year their marriage broke up.)

Mislio sam o tome prethodnih *godina*. (I had been thinking about it for the previous years.)

Kako je prošla *godina*? (How was the year?)